title: Open Bar #41 - Willow and Discovery Cancelled, Dungeons and Dragons Hates Men
description:

title: The Drinker Recommends... The Whale
description:
Brendan Fraser's seemingly unstoppable comeback continues with The Whale by Darren Aronofsky, which deservedly won him a Best Actor Oscar. 

Want to help support my work? Then check out my first comic book on Indiegogo: https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/first-kill-graphic-novel#/
